; bonker.scr 3/31/96

; ** Items

; robot cleaner for Demetrius's bar

INUMBER 844
NAME 726
*DESCRIPTION_START
All manner of cleaning utensils jut out of the vaguely humaniod form of
the robotic cleaner. Although it goes about its business as if nothing
was wrong, the majority of its cleaning tools have been broken off or
rotted away over the long course of its lifespan. Despite its
shortcomings, the robotic cleaner continues to struggle against the filth
that surrounds it with remarkable dedication and an almost human sense of
job satisfaction.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFTOUCH -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER As you reach out to touch the small robot, it lively zooms out of the way and continues its cleaning chores.
  ECHO OTHERS As %n reaches out to touch the small robot, it lively zooms out of the way and continues its cleaning chores.
ENDIF

