IFPREVERB WAVE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You shake up %a and watch the tiny scene inside the sphere become obscured in a gray cloud.
  ECHO OTHERS %n shakes up %a.
  PLREVENT 2
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER Slowly, you see the cloud begin to settle and snow falls on the tiny scene.
ENDIF

